data.description: Stunning 4BR/2BA Renovated Eastside Home! You will love the spacious Kitchen w/ Granite , Lots of  cabinets, Stainless Steel Fridgidare Appls. Pantry and Dining Area. Primary Suite has Luxe Bathroom w/ huge Tiled Double Shower w/ Bench, Ample Granite counter space, Dual sinks & lots of cabinets. Spacious Great room accents a Stacked Stone Fireplace and split plan features a Large 4th BR w/ walk in closet. Dual Pane windows, updated light fixtures & Ceiling fans, Laundry/ hobby  room W & D included. Photos are from 2019 purchase and have been purchased from photographer. 2019 painted interior & exterior. Water Harvesting, Fruit trees include: lime, lemon, pomegranite & orange. Close to Palo Verde Park. You will love this Home,
